==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: minuend
<hw>min"u*end</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>minuendus</ets> to be diminished, fr. <ets>minuere</ets> to lessen,
diminish. See <er>Minish</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Arith.)</fld> <def>In the
process of subtraction{2}, the number from which another number (the
<corr>subtrahend</corr>) is to be subtracted, to find the
<corr>difference</corr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

